Compress images with adjustable quality settings
Support JPG, PNG, static GIF, static WebP, HEIC, and AVIF input formats.
Batch process multiple images at once
Download individual images or as a zip archive
Capture photos directly (in mobile) and load them into crushmon
Rename, download, or delete images individually
Works fully offline after initial load
